ut that now, in the wake of the quagmire in Iraq, has returned to haunt America's post-9/11 "project for the new American century."  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 4aLiterature : American Literature. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / American / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978079147913140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791479131423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791479131/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles